code: import axios from'axios';var baseUrl='/api/persons';var getAll=function getAll(){var request=axios.get(baseUrl);return request.then(function(response){return response.data;});};var create=function create(newObject){var request=axios.post(baseUrl,newObject);return request.then(function(response){return response.data;});};var deletePerson=function deletePerson(id){var request=axios.delete(baseUrl+'/'+id);return request.then(function(response){return response.status;});};export default{getAll:getAll,create:create,deletePerson:deletePerson};
